{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-doc-page-js","path":"/docs/loaders","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Loaders</h1>\n<p>loaders are used when retrieving data or performing slow computations, and help to notify users\nthat loading is underway.</p>\n<h2>Demo</h2>\n<p>loaders has 2 sizes <code>c-loader--small</code> and <code>c-loader--large</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-loader c-loader--white-container c-loader--small<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-loader c-loader--white-container c-loader--large<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>loaders on white background</h3>\n<p>You can apply it using the <code>c-loader--white-container</code> modifier class</p>\n<div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex--row u-align-items--center u-window-padding--1x\">\n  <div class=\"u-display-flex u-flex-grow--1 u-justify-content--center u-align-items--cent